select 
adjuster_id,
adjuster_rut_num,
adjuster_name,
adjuster_type_desc,
adjuster_office_cd,
adjuster_office_name,
src_sys_cd,
actv_rec_ind,
max_sid
from(SELECT 
src.adjuster_id,
src.adjuster_rut_num,
src.adjuster_name,
src.adjuster_type_desc,
src.adjuster_office_cd,
src.adjuster_office_name,
src.src_sys_cd,
'Y' as actv_rec_ind,
LKP_MAXSID.max_sid,
ROW_NUMBER()OVER(PARtiTION BY src.adjuster_id order by src.rec_crt_dtm desc) rnk
FROM (
select 
cast('axis' as varchar(10)) as src_sys_cd,
A.adjuster_id,
A.adjuster_rut_num,
translate(A.adjuster_name,'#','') as adjuster_name,
CAST(A.CACTPRO AS VARCHAR(80)) adjuster_type_desc,
CAST(A.adjuster_office_cd AS VARCHAR(10)) adjuster_office_cd,
CAST(A.adjuster_office_name AS VARCHAR(100)) adjuster_office_name,
A.rec_crt_dtm,
1 dummy from
(select distinct 
CAST(l.SPERSON AS INTEGER) adjuster_id,
CAST(p.NNUMNIF AS VARCHAR(35)) adjuster_rut_num,
CAST(p.tbuscar AS VARCHAR(100)) adjuster_name,
CASE WHEN l.cactpro= 333 THEN 'Directo'
	 WHEN l.cactpro= 332 THEN 'Oficial'
	 ELSE NULL END CACTPRO,
'' adjuster_office_cd,
'' adjuster_office_name,
l.rec_crt_dtm	
from  cdp_stg_dwh.sisaxis_ASIGPROTRAMI l
INNER JOIN  cdp_ods.sisaxis_personas p
ON l.SPERSON = p.SPERSON 
WHERE l.CACTPRO in (332,333))A	
) src
left outer join
(select 1 as dummy, max(dim_claim_adjuster_key) as MAX_SID from cdp_dwh.dim_claim_adjuster_t) LKP_MAXSID
on src.dummy = LKP_MAXSID.dummy)
where rnk=1;

SELECT  
dim_claim_adjuster_key,
adjuster_id,
src_sys_cd  
FROM cdp_dwh.dim_claim_adjuster_t 
where src_sys_cd='axis';
